# User Schema

## User Models

The user system consists of several related models:

- @Local User - The main user model
  - Contains authentication data like Phone, Password
  - Connected to user info, addresses, wallet, etc.
  
- @Local User Info - User profile information
  - Contains FirstName, LastName, and other personal details
  
- @Local User Address - User shipping addresses
  - Contains address details for delivery and billing

- @Local User Role - User role assignments
  - Defines user permissions and access levels

## User Wallet

- @Local User Wallet - Digital wallet for users
  - Tracks user's account balance

- @Local User Wallet Transaction - Wallet transaction history
  - Records deposits, withdrawals, and other wallet transactions

## User Permissions

- @Local User Permission - Permission settings for users
  - Defines specific permissions for user actions and access

